dct_description_sm: Relief and depths shown by gradient tints. "Published May 2008." Includes notes, statistical tables, graphs, and key to pipeline projects. Insets: Oil and gas map of the Caspian Sea -- Principal pipilenes projects in Caspian and Black sea area -- Energy infrastructure of Ukraine & Black sea.
